[[File:Unknown_Kamino_droid_1.jpg|thumb|right|250px|[[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and [[Aayla Secura/Legends|Aayla Secura]] repair a hermit crab droid on [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]].]]

'''Hermit crab droids''' were small, [[Crab/Legends|crablike]] [[Droid/Legends|droids]] with six [[Limb/Legends|legs]] and two stalked [[Photoreceptor/Legends|eyes]]. In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] attempted to fix one of these droids that was found on [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]] during the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] briefing before the upcoming [[First Battle of Kamino|battle]], but [[Aayla Secura/Legends|Aayla Secura]] showed Skywalker that the droid simply wasn't turned on.

